name: Reciprocative Aubjkt
description:
I was given an aubjkt therefore I had to make an aubjkt.
Usual process, Panasonic SDR-S7 'filming' an eggplant from the grocery store on Source 3. Panasonic AG-MX70 self feedback into Source 1. Chroma Keying. Trimmed in LiVES, frames extracted with ffmpeg, gif edited in GiMP.
